graph TD
    A[Input Data] --> B[Hash Function]
    B --> C{Hash Table}
    C --> |Index 0| D[Bucket 0]
    C --> |Index 1| E[Bucket 1]
    C --> |Index 2| F[Bucket 2]
    C --> |...| G[...]
    C --> |Index n-1| H[Bucket n-1]
    
    I[Collision Resolution] --> |Chaining| J[Linked List]
    I --> |Open Addressing| K[Probing]
    
    L[Operations] --> M[Insert]
    L --> N[Search]
    L --> O[Delete]
    
    P[Load Factor] --> Q[Resize/Rehash]
